casebody.head_matter:
Gary OTTE, petitioner,
v.
OHIO.
No. 16-9317 (17A136).
Supreme Court of the United States
Sept. 12, 2017.
Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice KAGAN and by her referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Ohio denied.
